A minimalistic Bitcoin seed phrase generator based on the BIP-39 standard.  
Built for learning, hacking, and experimenting with Bitcoin internals ⚡🧠

## Features 🧬
- Generates 12 / 24 word mnemonic seed phrases 🔑
- BIP-39 compliant English wordlist 📜
- Fast, simple, and lightweight ⚙️

## Warning ⚠️
This project is for **educational purposes only**.  
Do **NOT** use generated seed phrases to secure real Bitcoin 💀💸  
If you lose your seed — you lose your coins. No exceptions.

## Security Rules 🔒
- Never share your seed phrase 🤫  
- Never store it online ☁️🚫  
- Trust no one. Verify everything 🕵️‍♂️

## Philosophy 🧠
Not your keys — not your coins.

